1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,800
Pedaleando entre jardines...

2
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:02,800
y de repente,

3
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:03,800
algo en la acera.

4
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:04,720
Estoy cruzando el Turia

5
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:05,600
en bici.

6
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:06,320
Es esa hora

7
00:00:06,320 --> 00:00:07,160
en la que el parque

8
00:00:07,160 --> 00:00:07,920
se llena de gente

9
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:08,480
paseando,

10
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:08,920
de luz

11
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,200
entre los árboles.

12
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:10,880
Noto el olor

13
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:11,840
a tierra húmeda,

14
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:12,760
las sombras largas

15
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:13,680
en el camino.

16
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,640
Y entonces llegas

17
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:15,720
al Jardín Real.

18
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,240
Todo el mundo

19
00:00:16,240 --> 00:00:16,600
lo conoce,

20
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:17,000
claro.

21
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:17,800
Pero en bici,

22
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:18,280
a esta hora,

23
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:18,840
te fijas

24
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:20,080
en cosas distintas.

25
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:20,560
Las palmeras

26
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:21,640
desde abajo,

27
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:23,000
un banco vacío.

28
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:23,960
Silencio.

29
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,040
Bajo unas escaleras,

30
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:26,280
paso por delante

31
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:26,560
del Palau

32
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:27,600
de la Música.

33
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:28,320
De parque en parque

34
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,040
en bici

35
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:29,920
por Valencia,

36
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:31,640
siempre descubres algo.

37
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,480
Y me pregunto...

38
00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:33,560
¿cuánta gente pasa

39
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:34,280
por estos parques

40
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:34,960
cada día

41
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:35,920
sin fijarse?

42
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:36,520
Hay estatuas,

43
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,280
rincones verdes,

44
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,240
calles que huelen

45
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:38,720
a naranjo.

46
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:39,800
Todo ahí,

47
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,920
esperando.

48
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:41,640
Y justo ahí,

49
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,120
en la acera

50
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,000
de Jaime Roig...

51
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,280
una silla de oficina.

52
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:44,760
Negra,

53
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:45,840
completa,

54
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:47,120
con todas las ruedas.

55
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:47,600
Esto no tendría

56
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,800
que estar aquí.

57
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,200
Si alguien

58
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,000
hubiera sabido

59
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,080
que otra persona

60
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:51,560
la quiere,

61
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:52,480
habría llegado directa

62
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,320
a su nueva casa.

63
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,240
Yo lo que hice

64
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,200
fue pararme,

65
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,160
sacar el móvil,

66
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,360
subirla a Givore.

67
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:58,800
Barrio,

68
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,640
foto,

69
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,400
listo.

70
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,360
Y seguí pedaleando.

71
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:02,600
Si tenéis algo en casa

72
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,320
que ya no usáis...

73
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,600
pensad en la silla.

74
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:05,800
A veces solo falta

75
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:06,840
que alguien conecte.

